+python -m compileall -q src tests tools
+python -m pytest -q \
+  tests/tools/test_plan_context_recall_integration_0214.py \
+  tests/rules/test_context_recall_integration_plan_0214_rule.py
+python -m pytest -q tests/rules
+python -m pytest -q
+```
